OL,4,Cunimaginable in court for the final
OL,5,Ctime
OL,7,FFor the final time, Gisele Pelicot
OL,8,Fcarried herself calmly into court to
OL,9,Fface the unimaginable: a room filled
OL,10,Fwith dozens of men who raped her while
OL,11,Fshe lay unconscious.
OL,13,FAt the centre of it all - sitting in a
OL,14,Fglass dock - was her ex-husband
OL,15,FDominique Pelicot.
