OL,7,FI saw several that had come with wives
OL,8,Fand girlfriends kissing and hugging
OL,9,Fthem goodbye before walking into the
OL,10,Fhearing room.
OL,12,FAll 50 received some form of guilty
OL,13,Fverdict - the majority for aggravated
OL,14,Frape. But their sentences, which
OL,15,Franged from three to 15 years,
OL,16,Ffrequently fell below what prosecutors
OL,17,Fhad asked for.
