OL,7,FGisele Pelicot told reporters
OL,8,Fafterwards that she respected the
OL,9,Fdecision of the court, but her
OL,10,Fchildren are understood to be unhappy
OL,11,Fwith the length of those sentences.
OL,13,FLawyers representing some of those men
OL,14,Fhave said that their clients intend to
OL,15,Fappeal. They now have 10 days to
OL,16,Fdecide.
OL,18,FAfter nearly four months of evidence,
OL,19,Fthis trial has raised more questions
OL,20,Fthan it has answers.
